snippet: Shanghai Bobby, undefeated in five starts, held off He’s Had Enough to win the Juvenile and allow Rosie Napravnik to join Julie Krone as the only female jockeys to win Breeders’ Cup races.
lead_paragraph: Shanghai Bobby, undefeated in five starts, held off He’s Had Enough to win the Juvenile and allow Rosie Napravnik to join Julie Krone as the only female jockeys to win Breeders’ Cup races.

headline.seo: Shanghai Bobby and Rosie Napravnik Add Breeders’ Cup Wins to Records
headline.main: Unbeaten Shanghai Bobby Adds Breeders’ Cup Win
headline.print_headline: Unbeaten Shanghai Bobby Adds Breeders’ Cup Win
